commitResults.messageBody:
The AboutUs.md is missing information.

The information is outdated and uses
placeholder information.

Let's edit the AboutUs with my information.

This way users can understand who I am.

The README does not have our project's
name nor updated UI mockup.

Let's edit  the content of the README.

This is so that users get the updated
overview of our product.

The DeveloperGuide is missing relevant
use cases.

Let's add the relevant minimal use cases.

Use case has borderline UI ideas and misses
full stop.

However, use case must not have any UI ideas.

Let's rephrase 'type commands' to 'request' 
and add full stops.
Let's add the mark attendance use case.

FindCommand does not list out persons whose
partial name matches the keyword.

Users may not recall the proper first or
last name and thus might have troubles
locating contacts.

Let's edit containsWordIgnoreCase method
to check if substrings of Person list names
match user's input.
Fixed attribute length to correct CI length check failure.
Minor edits to Message attribute for checkstyle purpose.
Let's fix trailing whitespace for Name.java

commitResults.messageBody:
Find command could only find matches for
partial name. Howvever, one may only
remember the tag given or partial phone
number so find will not be useful if
it can only find using names.

Let's create 3 different find commands and
related classes so that we can find name,
find tag, find phone.
